{lang-eng}We’re here to praise our Savior,
The wonderful Lord of all
We eat, we drink, we live,
We breathe, we dwell in Him.
We magnify Him;
He’s our all in all;
He is our strength;
We cannot fall
Because, because, because,
Because, because —-
Because of the wonderful
Way He loves!  (Brothers-hold,
